text: West Malling is a small market town in Tonbridge and Malling, Kent, England. Its postcode is ME19. There are many historical sites in West Malling that make it a popular place to visit. There are many shops. There is a population of between 3,000 and 5,000 people. St Mary's Church is at the top of the High Street. Category:Towns in Kent
title: West Malling
